OL,7,FSouthern Water has been fined #330,000
OL,8,Fafter raw sewage escaped into a stream
OL,9,Fnear Southampton for what the company
OL,10,Fadmitted could have been nearly 20
OL,11,Fhours.
OL,13,FAlmost 2,000 fish were killed as
OL,14,Ffaulty equipment at a pumping station
OL,15,Fsent untreated effluent into the
OL,16,Fenvironment at Waltham Chase on the
OL,17,Fedge of the South Downs.
