OL,7,FSitting at West Hampshire magistrates'
OL,8,Fcourt, district judge Nicholas Wattam
OL,9,Fheard relay equipment at Little Bull
OL,10,Fpumping station had been wrongly
OL,11,Fprogrammed.
OL,13,FThis led to a pump failing. When a
OL,14,Fsecond one wouldn't start, sewage and
OL,15,Fother hazardous substances were
OL,16,Fdiverted up through two manholes,
OL,17,Facross fields and into Shawford Lake
OL,18,FStream, leading to the popular YMCA
OL,19,FFairthorne Manor.
