OL,7,FIn the days after the incident in July
OL,8,F2019, investigators from the
OL,9,FEnvironment Agency found pools of
OL,10,Fdirty water and polluted matter and
OL,11,Fvegetation in local fields.
OL,13,FThe stream was cloudy as pollution
OL,14,Fspread across nearly 3km. Ammonia
OL,15,Flevels in the water were 25 times the
OL,16,Flegal limit.
OL,18,FScores of brown trout and other dead
OL,19,Ffish continued to be discovered. Tens
OL,20,Fbecame hundreds as the scale of the
OL,21,Fpollution emerged.
