OL,7,FInvestigators believe the illegal flow
OL,8,Fof contaminated matter continued over
OL,9,Fpublic land and the stream for between
OL,10,Ffive and 20 hours.
OL,12,FDawn Theaker, environment manager in
OL,13,FHampshire for the Environment Agency,
OL,14,Fsaid: "We prosecuted Southern Water
OL,15,Fbecause of environmental harm caused
OL,16,Fby the pollution, a direct result of
OL,17,Fnegligence in how the pumping station
OL,18,Fwas managed.
