OL,7,F"We are delivering the changes people
OL,8,Fwant to see: more investment, stronger
OL,9,Fregulation and tougher enforcement on
OL,10,Fwater companies. This includes our
OL,11,Fproposals to ban water company
OL,12,Fexecutive bonuses, and we recently
OL,13,Fgave the Environment Agency greater
OL,14,Fpowers to impose uncapped civil
OL,15,Fpenalties on polluters."
