OL,7,FThe Environment Agency first heard
OL,8,Fsomething was wrong from a member of
OL,9,Fthe public around noon on that
OL,10,Fsummer's day in 2019, saying he saw
OL,11,Funtreated sewage, solids and tissue
OL,12,Fentering the stream.
OL,14,FAn alarm on the failed pump went off
OL,15,Fjust after 7am, but Southern Water had
OL,16,Ffailed to act on it.
