OL,7,FThe Environment Agency sent an officer
OL,8,Fto the scene in response to the first
OL,9,Freport and fed back that the stream
OL,10,Falongside the pumping station was
OL,11,Fcloudy, and there was a definite smell
OL,12,Fin the air.
OL,14,FThe officer saw sewage debris had
OL,15,Fcollected around one manhole in a
OL,16,Ffield and then evidence of sewage
OL,17,Fcoming out of another nearby.
OL,19,FHe also saw the first of many dead
OL,20,Ffish as a result of the pollution.
