OL,7,FThe number of fish killed grew as the
OL,8,Finvestigation went on. Brown trout,
OL,9,Fbullheads and sticklebacks all found
OL,10,Flifeless in the water ` 1,954 in all.
OL,11,FInvestigators saw no live fish in
OL,12,Fparts of the stream, only dead ones.
OL,14,FSouthern Water pleaded guilty at an
OL,15,Fearlier hearing to one breach of the
OL,16,FEnvironmental Permitting (England and
OL,17,FWales) Regulations 2016 regarding the
OL,18,Fpollution and operation of Little Bull
OL,19,Fpumping station on or around 21 July
OL,20,F2019.
