OL,12,Fenvironmental harm.
OL,14,F"We took immediate action to reduce
OL,15,Fthe impact in the local area and have
OL,16,Fco-operated consistently with the
OL,17,FEnvironment Agency throughout their
OL,18,Finvestigation and pleaded guilty at
OL,19,Fthe earliest opportunity.
